嵐山の桂川両岸に咲く桜を照らす午後の太陽。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Afternoon sun illuminates cherry blossoms on both sides of the Katsura River in Arashiyama. 嵐山の桂川両岸に咲く桜を照らす午後の太陽。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_DSCF7563-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_DSCF7563-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Osawa Pond・大沢池</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230327/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Osawa Pond・大沢池" /><published>2023-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/daikakuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230327/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Cherry trees in bloom at the Osawa Ike pond at Daikaku-ji temple.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
大覚寺の大沢池に桜が咲いています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Ponds" /><summary type="html">Cherry trees in bloom at the Osawa Ike pond at Daikaku-ji temple. 大覚寺の大沢池に桜が咲いています。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_A7R06995-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_A7R06995-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nakanoshima・中之島</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230326/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nakanoshima・中之島" /><published>2023-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nakanoshima</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230326/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
