&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Rain" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Dripping pink weeping cherry blossoms in front of the more traditional Yoshino-Zakura trees, on a rainy morning on Arashiyama’s Nakanoshima Island. 雨の朝、嵐山・中之島にある伝統的な吉野桜の前に、滴るようなピンクの枝垂れ桜がある。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_A7R06937-2-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_A7R06937-2-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyama Sakura・嵐山の桜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230324/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyama Sakura・嵐山の桜" /><published>2023-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230324/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Cherry blossoms are now coming out in Arashiyama as well, recent warm weather accelerating the rush to open. Still a ways to go until full bloom.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
嵐山でも桜が咲き始め,完全開花まではまだ時間がかかりそうです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms are now coming out in Arashiyama as well, recent warm weather accelerating the rush to open. Still a ways to go until full bloom. 嵐山でも桜が咲き始め,完全開花まではまだ時間がかかりそうです。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_IMG_7574-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2303_IMG_7574-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Cherry Trees・桜の木</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230323/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cherry Trees・桜の木" /><published>2023-03-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-03-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/cherrytree</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230323/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
